{"tid":1605492,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[同我推上熱門]咁簡單嘅動作啲狗就會驚㗎啦","createTime":"2019-09-30T10:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:05:46.000Z","uid":4854,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c349e6a25601f9f545a97e531cfa97e9af0cb69","tid":1605492,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/219478461572330/posts/1186805461506287?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F219478461572330%2Fposts%2F1186805461506287%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=7c6cd5de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/219478461572330/posts/1186805461506287?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n只要有10個以上手足衝番上去圍啲狗<br />\n其實咩都唔使做只係用把遮打左佢一下<br />\n個防暴第一個反應已經嚇到彈開<br />\n隻速龍雖然舉左槍<br />\n如果各位手足個個開傘嘅話<br />\n已經可以完美掩護救人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家聽日係走嘅時候睇吓有冇機會吹雞救翻啲落單手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"6a92b1101516ee41d85bc159b23258a6be3d7308","tid":1605492,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"推上去比多啲前線手足見到"},{"pid":"97eeb7fd2b911135f58beb3a93c01846b4d22b15","tid":1605492,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"推上去比多啲前線手足見到x2"},{"pid":"280a61fe80ec449cd1259f596cac589c05628d3c","tid":1605492,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"推上去比多啲前線手足見到x3"},{"pid":"0c97d84bdf3767b9a61bd97f900055cb36cff574","tid":1605492,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"推上去比多啲前線手足見到x4"},{"pid":"588f566803049c29534269a13f8eafeecc5956f0","tid":1605492,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:02:40.000Z","msg":"推上去比多啲